        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 7 at 8:21PM CDT until July 7 at 8:45PM CDT by NWS Hastings NE</headline>
        <description>SVRGID

The National Weather Service in Hastings has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
Northeastern Greeley County in central Nebraska...

* Until 845 PM CDT.

* At 821 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Spalding, or
18 miles west of Albion, moving northeast at 20 mph.

HAZARD...Quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

* This severe thunderstorm will be near...
Spalding around 825 PM CDT.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
